Tanıtılan 📢 T409E Electric Material Handler in Stock – Ready to Ship!
Looking for a powerful, eco-friendly solution? The T409E material handler is 100% electric and packed with cutting-edge features designed for efficiency and performance. With powerful AC Motor – 50kW power for up to 9 hours of operation, 4 Operating Speeds, 33-Foot Reach & 16'5” Cab Elevation there is no better electric material handler!

 Act now! The T409E is ready to be delivered!

Tanıtılan 🛠️ Are you a processor? We know how hard and dangerous your job is. 
For more than 35 years, we have been working with the same daily challenges that you know well, which is why worker safety is a priority for us.

With our balers and shear balers, we guarantee maximum safety and efficiency. Our aim is to make your work easier by providing reliable, quality solutions. 

Find out more on our website: https://lnkd.in/gvMYwMGb
#GPSforScrapyard #scrapyardsafety #heavyequipment #efficiency #quality #safety #hardwork #scrapyardsolutions #innovation #gpsrecycling

Tanıtılan 🌐🏭 The Destroyer marks a momentous turning point in the scrap metal recycling industry. It is the first real innovation in the industry in the last 10 years, and is the most powerful wing shear ever. 
The force applied to the lids clearly exceeds traditional shears. In addition, its wide loading area of over 2.8 metres, with one side open, allows the easy handling of the bulkiest material.

Thanks to the state-of-the-art hydraulic power unit, we guarantee maximum production efficiency at a reduced cost per tonne.

Learn more about how this innovation is changing the scrap recycling industry. https://lnkd.in/gAfnKPG7

#DestroyerInnovation #SustainableRecycling #ProductiveEfficiency

Tanıtılan A success story – behind-the-scenes at #Liebherr!

What accounts for our success over decades? 
In an conversation, two members of the Liebherr-International AG board of directors, together with two contemporary witnesses, reflect on the courage to innovate, lived values, and the "Liebherr spirit." 

They share their experiences and insights that have shaped the success story and take a look at the visions for the future. A call to all those who want to actively shape change! 💡🔧

Tanıtılan 🤝 Was uns auszeichnet und hervorhebt?
Als innovatives Familienunternehmen stellen wir gute Ideen vor Berufstitel. Wir leben eine Atmosphäre von gegenseitigem Respekt, Fair Play und der Leidenschaft für Technologie, die den Unterschied macht. 

Ihre Vorteile:
• Vielfältige Positionen in der Elektrotechnik
• Kollegialität: Arbeiten Sie in einem Team, das Zusammenarbeit und Familienunternehmen lebt
• Entwicklungsmöglichkeiten: ein umfangreiches Weiterbildungsangebot und die Vielfältigkeit unserer Firmengruppe

Werden Sie ein Teil von uns.
